# ── LLM API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Add one or more API keys below.
# The app automatically decides the mode based on how many keys you add:
#
#   1 key  → runs that model only
#   2 keys → runs both in parallel and correlates results
#   3 keys → full 3-way correlation (highest confidence)
#
# No toggles, no extra config — just add your keys.

# Anthropic — direct Claude access
# Get key: https://console.anthropic.com  ($5 free credits on signup)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6

# OpenRouter — access to 100+ models via one key
# Get key: https://openrouter.ai  (free credits on signup)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=anthropic/claude-3-haiku

# Google Gemini — direct Gemini access
# Get key: https://aistudio.google.com  (free tier available)
# GEMINI_API_KEY=...
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-flash

# ── Kubernetes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
KUBECONFIG=~/.kube/config

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DB_PATH=k8s_debugger.db

# ── Argo CD (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# When set, investigations also include ArgoCD app health + sync status.
# ARGOCD_URL=https://your-argocd-server.example.com
# ARGOCD_TOKEN=your_argocd_api_token
# ARGOCD_USERNAME=admin
# ARGOCD_PASSWORD=your_password
